[{"id":"VH912483","type":"mcq","stimulusHtml":"<p class=\"stem_paragraph\">A <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1 liter\"><math alttext=\"1 liter\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>1</mn><mspace depth=\"0.0ex\" height=\"0.0ex\" width=\"0.25em\"></mspace><mtext>L</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> sample of helium gas at <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"25 degrees Celsius\"><math alttext=\"25 degrees Celsius\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>25</mn><mi>°</mi><mtext>C</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1 atmosphere\"><math alttext=\"1 atmosphere\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>1</mn><mspace depth=\"0.0ex\" height=\"0.0ex\" width=\"0.25em\"></mspace><mtext>atm</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> is combined with a <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1 liter\"><math alttext=\"1 liter\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>1</mn><mspace depth=\"0.0ex\" height=\"0.0ex\" width=\"0.25em\"></mspace><mtext>L</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> sample of neon gas at <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"25 degrees Celsius\"><math alttext=\"25 degrees Celsius\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>25</mn><mi>°</mi><mtext>C</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> and <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"1 atmosphere\"><math alttext=\"1 atmosphere\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mn>1</mn><mspace depth=\"0.0ex\" height=\"0.0ex\" width=\"0.25em\"></mspace><mtext>atm</mtext></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span>. The temperature is kept constant. Which of the following statements about combining the gases is correct?</p>\n","rubricRef":"VH912483_rubric","choicesHtml":["<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The average speed of the helium atoms increases when the gases are combined.</